Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.72,0:02:33.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.20,0:02:34.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.18,0:02:36.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我今天不吃早饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.40,0:02:38.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去学校了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.86,0:02:39.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.90,0:02:43.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.84,0:02:44.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生什么事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.98,0:02:48.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没 偶尔早点去学校也不错
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.34,0:02:49.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我上学去了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.68,0:02:56.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须扔了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.22,0:02:58.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要把这个扔了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.48,0:03:00.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切就都结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.94,0:03:07.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  变熟练了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.10,0:04:06.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很温柔对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.76,0:04:16.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里啊  真的好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.40,0:04:18.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿  我是小津
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.88,0:04:20.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小津三郎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.96,0:04:22.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是叫你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.86,0:04:32.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你喜欢什么味道的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.56,0:04:34.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芝麻味
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.26,0:04:35.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芝麻味？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.30,0:04:37.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打铃了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.34,0:04:38.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.82,0:04:39.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天也要迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.84,0:04:41.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛  没事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.80,0:04:42.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春日君
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.68,0:04:51.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作文写好了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.62,0:04:53.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,写好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.16,0:05:00.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天放学后也到图书室来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.02,0:05:10.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春日
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.74,0:05:24.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天要进行避难训练
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.72,0:05:26.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记得带防灾头巾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.06,0:05:28.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.84,0:05:31.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经无处可逃了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.62,0:05:35.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐伯同学
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.84,0:05:38.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我...我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.50,0:05:49.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有一件事要告诉大家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.54,0:05:53.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于前几天佐伯同学的体操服被偷的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.36,0:05:55.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实那天放学后
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.62,0:05:59.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有本校的学生看到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.36,0:06:01.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学校周围有可疑的男子在徘徊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.48,0:06:07.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貌似是三十岁左右的长发眼镜男
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.56,0:06:10.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 安静
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.48,0:06:12.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安静
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.30,0:06:15.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果看见可疑人员马上向老师汇报
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.60,0:06:18.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放学后立刻回家
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.72,0:06:19.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.00,0:06:22.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶紧抓住犯人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.32,0:06:25.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌  我如果被做了奇怪的事情该怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.98,0:06:28.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春日  变有趣了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.60,0:06:31.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春日？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.22,0:06:36.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈奈子  别太在意了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.68,0:07:14.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是魔头
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.68,0:07:19.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,掌控着我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.58,0:07:22.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生命线啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.12,0:07:28.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,令我们沉溺于罪恶的美色靡靡之中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.08,0:07:31.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每日一步步
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.02,0:07:34.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迈入地狱的深渊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.82,0:07:38.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毫无惊悚地穿过
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.20,0:07:42.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,散发着恶臭的黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.92,0:08:05.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春日君
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.30,0:08:08.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快让我看看作文
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.38,0:08:18.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.98,0:08:21.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,波尔莱尔的诗集
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.94,0:08:22.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恶之花
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.18,0:08:25.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我最喜欢的诗集
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.42,0:08:28.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这本书中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.82,0:08:30.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,流淌蔓延着阴暗的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.30,0:08:32.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是生活在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.90,0:08:33.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平凡的这些家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.42,0:08:36.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一辈子都无法理解的哲学
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.64,0:08:39.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是我的化身
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.30,0:08:42.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是我的作文
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.66,0:08:45.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴 臭虫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.60,0:08:47.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春日君
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.12,0:08:50.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想看的是将春日君激昂呐喊的内心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.66,0:08:52.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赤裸裸地表现出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.02,0:08:54.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,充满扭曲幻想的作文
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.86,0:08:57.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春日君　你不是把脸埋在佐伯的双峰之间了么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.62,0:08:59.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是每天在家贪婪地吸吮着运动服的香气么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.42,0:09:01.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是用体操服在你邪恶的身体上四处摩擦么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.78,0:09:03.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不就是这么一个彻底的大变态么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.54,0:09:04.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春日君
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.56,0:09:07.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.42,0:09:11.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我根本就听不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.92,0:09:13.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天也是 今天也是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.72,0:09:15.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在想些什么 仲村
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.16,0:09:17.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时教室的气氛没看到么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.16,0:09:19.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可疑的家伙是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.18,0:09:21.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连佐伯同学都用可疑的眼神看着我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.44,0:09:23.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.14,0:09:25.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本就不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.70,0:09:27.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.66,0:09:29.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才没有用运动服到处乱蹭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.16,0:09:31.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐伯同学
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.24,0:09:32.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我的缪斯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.56,0:09:33.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的女神
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.74,0:09:34.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的玛利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.24,0:09:35.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我的维纳斯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.58,0:09:36.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永远都是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.32,0:09:37.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个东西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.84,0:09:39.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个东西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.86,0:09:41.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在就扔进焚烧炉烧掉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.96,0:09:46.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.22,0:09:50.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等　等等
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.56,0:09:51.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.58,0:09:54.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.80,0:09:58.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要　停手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.96,0:10:06.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.96,0:10:07.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.32,0:10:42.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.20,0:10:46.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.26,0:10:50.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春日君
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.88,0:10:51.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.72,0:10:55.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很久以前就觉得身体里充斥着躁动
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.00,0:11:02.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至想将身体深处的欲望大声呐喊出来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.28,0:11:03.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种躁动难以忍耐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.54,0:11:06.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至觉得整个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.38,0:11:08.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都在我难耐的躁动中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.88,0:11:10.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去死的话比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.76,0:11:20.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我肯定也是个变态
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.36,0:11:23.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.68,0:11:28.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春日君
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.38,0:11:29.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要有信心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.14,0:11:31.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能和我签订契约的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.08,0:11:33.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有春日君
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.38,0:11:42.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以后 每天放学以后都和我一起过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.76,0:11:43.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这么定了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.16,0:11:51.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐伯同学的体操服
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.48,0:11:53.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紧紧地贴着我的皮肤
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.92,0:11:55.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悄然地
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.14,0:11:57.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,散发出罪恶之香
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.52,0:12:11.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 春日
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.36,0:12:12.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去我家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.46,0:12:13.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.60,0:12:16.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我今天有事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.74,0:12:18.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么这样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.78,0:12:21.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近根本没一起玩嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.38,0:12:23.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了算了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.40,0:12:25.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管了 那样的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.52,0:12:59.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.88,0:13:09.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从那之后一个礼拜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.02,0:13:11.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和仲村
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.14,0:13:14.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放学后每天都一起度过
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.98,0:13:22.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.96,0:13:26.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 那么正大光明的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.90,0:13:28.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,万一被学校那帮家伙发现的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.52,0:13:30.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道被说成什么样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.96,0:13:31.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那又怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.06,0:13:35.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还说“怎样”
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.82,0:13:38.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 快一点 春日君
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.30,0:13:58.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 春日君
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.94,0:14:01.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近我的手的味道很好闻哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.82,0:14:03.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闻闻看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.96,0:14:04.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.08,0:14:12.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,流经小镇的最大的河
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.10,0:14:17.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那条河的草丛中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.46,0:14:21.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听着仲村那些虚幻的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.12,0:14:32.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 天已经很暗了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.52,0:14:35.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天差不多就
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.20,0:14:39.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你爸妈不会生气吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.10,0:14:42.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每天都这么晚回家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.22,0:14:43.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手借我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.86,0:14:44.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.54,0:14:57.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.32,0:15:01.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春日用这手在佐伯的体操服上来回抚摸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.92,0:15:04.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在身上四处摩擦来着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.78,0:15:06.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说我没有做这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.20,0:15:07.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变态
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.88,0:15:11.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你喜欢佐伯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.30,0:15:13.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢她哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.70,0:15:16.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时候穿着佐伯的体操服
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.92,0:15:18.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.46,0:15:19.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兴奋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.08,0:15:22.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,写不了作文的话口述吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.50,0:15:24.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这变态
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.78,0:15:25.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.64,0:15:26.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.32,0:15:27.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说啊 你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.56,0:15:30.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说啊 你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.70,0:15:32.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的 停手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.14,0:15:43.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.58,0:15:48.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 我想今天真的先回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.34,0:15:51.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天也变暗了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.52,0:16:12.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天就回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.80,0:16:14.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.82,0:16:28.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.98,0:16:30.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每天都跑去哪里了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.46,0:16:31.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.42,0:16:34.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和山田玩稍微玩了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.30,0:16:36.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么呀 有这么玩的必要吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.76,0:16:39.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和你爸爸都没吃饭在等你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.82,0:16:40.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了好了 老婆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.30,0:16:43.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高男已经是中学生了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.26,0:16:44.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玩玩不是也挺好的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.32,0:16:45.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老公
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.38,0:16:46.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.34,0:16:47.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.74,0:16:51.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你妈也是担心你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.86,0:16:54.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次至少打个电话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.38,0:16:59.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 快吃饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.88,0:17:08.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在做什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.96,0:17:21.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还残留着
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.12,0:17:22.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仲村的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.36,0:17:29.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仲村到底想做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.76,0:17:33.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对仲村来说我算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.78,0:17:39.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.94,0:17:43.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,整个世界都在我难耐的躁动中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.40,0:17:45.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去死的话比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.66,0:17:47.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仲村大概
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.96,0:17:49.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.74,0:17:53.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用和我一样的想法生存着
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.24,0:17:57.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定也是变态
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.12,0:18:02.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.14,0:18:05.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我不是变态
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.32,0:18:08.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对佐伯的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.84,0:18:10.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有对她的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.72,0:18:14.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是如此的纯粹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.04,0:18:27.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春日 早
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.42,0:18:29.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吵啊 一大早的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.38,0:18:31.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 其实啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.20,0:18:34.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在我哥哥房间里发现了DVD
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.94,0:18:38.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 懂得吧 DVD
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.58,0:18:40.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.46,0:18:41.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天来我家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.24,0:18:43.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.84,0:18:44.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.76,0:18:47.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么这样　来嘛春日
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.92,0:18:48.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妨碍我读书了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.70,0:18:49.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.34,0:18:53.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不见了 怎么办亚衣酱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.58,0:18:55.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.20,0:18:57.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真由冷静下来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.80,0:18:58.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么没了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.28,0:19:00.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,午餐费
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.58,0:19:03.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天忘记交就塞到储物柜里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.28,0:19:04.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天早上来了就没了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.10,0:19:05.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.70,0:19:08.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.26,0:19:15.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是有人昨天放学后偷的咯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.56,0:19:16.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.48,0:19:18.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上次才刚刚发生佐伯的事情不久
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.24,0:19:21.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.42,0:19:23.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁知道些什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.20,0:19:26.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.68,0:19:30.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会不会是仲村
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.28,0:19:32.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 山田
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.92,0:19:33.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仲村？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.64,0:19:36.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.74,0:19:40.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仲村
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.72,0:19:42.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.98,0:19:46.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仲村很可疑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.72,0:19:50.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.46,0:19:53.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仲村一直和我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.00,0:20:01.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 仲村
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.02,0:20:04.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你昨天放学做什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.06,0:20:08.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真由由的午餐费被偷了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.34,0:20:11.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仲村 你做了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.04,0:20:14.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你挡路了 滚开
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.12,0:20:14.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.60,0:20:15.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.80,0:20:18.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说 说起来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.20,0:20:21.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你昨天放学后打算回教室的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.72,0:20:22.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看见了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.88,0:20:24.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.72,0:20:25.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.78,0:20:26.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.66,0:20:29.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从以前开始就很奇怪啊你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.84,0:20:31.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直一个人碎碎念
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.42,0:20:32.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.96,0:20:33.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.58,0:20:34.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.68,0:20:40.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.76,0:20:44.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实不知道仲村在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.48,0:20:46.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是这次的事和她没关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.82,0:20:48.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,证据都没有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.80,0:20:53.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么呀 春日
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.74,0:20:56.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到一边看你的书去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.90,0:21:02.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说 春日
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.50,0:21:05.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你喜欢仲村啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.16,0:21:07.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人 真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.54,0:21:11.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春日
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.62,0:21:12.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好恐怖
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.96,0:21:14.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.36,0:21:15.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会选仲村啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.54,0:21:17.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春日 你很奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.26,0:21:18.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.46,0:21:19.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.98,0:21:22.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把客观的考察情况后的结果
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.78,0:23:23.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么我会那样说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.96,0:23:26.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.98,0:23:31.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隐藏了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.20,0:21:29.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真由 去和老师说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.70,0:23:24.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在冷静下想想
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.50,0:23:26.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷静
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.30,0:23:29.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,客观来看现在的状况
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.70,0:23:32.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道 已经发现了
